Do you know why I love lollipops?

18
00:02:06,723 --> 00:02:10,142
When I was little, my mom got sick.

19
00:02:10,142 --> 00:02:14,323
She had to take medicine every day, and my dad bought her lollipops every day.

20
00:02:14,323 --> 00:02:18,343
Whenever I was upset, my mom would give me her lollipop.

21
00:02:18,343 --> 00:02:22,383
