24
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:36,460
I thought once I grow up and earn money, life would be better.

25
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:40,345
But who knows it gets harder when I get older.

26
00:02:40,345 --> 00:02:44,105
It's still bitter after I eat a lollipop.

27
00:02:48,463 --> 00:02:51,703
Then you should thank these lollipops.

28
00:02:51,703 --> 00:02:54,343
You don't show any of the bitterness.

29
00:02:56,243 --> 00:03:00,163
Do you think we've grown up now?

30
00:03:01,143 --> 00:03:03,903
We grew up the moment we graduated from college.

31
00:03:03,903 --> 00:03:07,523
It's harder when we get older.

32
00:03:07,523 --> 00:03:08,843
Let's hang up now.

33
