36
00:03:19,863 --> 00:03:22,223
Maybe they just lost their love.

37
00:03:24,163 --> 00:03:27,383
Maybe they got their credit card bills.

38
00:03:27,383 --> 00:03:30,063
Maybe they just got scolded by their boss.

39
00:03:30,063 --> 00:03:32,303
Maybe they just met someone they like.

40
00:03:32,303 --> 00:03:35,160
Maybe they met someone they like but are too scared to confess.

41
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:38,685
Maybe they just made a completely different choice.

42
00:03:38,685 --> 00:03:42,345
Just like these mystery box lollipops,

43
