His birthday is tomorrow. Why do you make a cake today?

104
00:08:31,463 --> 00:08:35,383
We'd celebrate at midnight.

105
00:08:36,683 --> 00:08:39,692
All right, that's all for today.

106
00:08:39,692 --> 00:08:43,350
Still, put practical operation first.

107
00:08:44,123 --> 00:08:48,303
Lin Tuo, send the meeting minutes to the group in half an hour.

