144
00:11:40,903 --> 00:11:44,363
Okay, send it to the group then. Remember to remind our leader, bye.

145
00:11:44,363 --> 00:11:46,083
Bye.

146
00:11:50,283 --> 00:11:52,143
Can you go now?

147
00:11:52,143 --> 00:11:54,323
Senior, I haven't finished yet.

148
00:11:54,323 --> 00:11:55,643
What's it?

149
00:11:55,643 --> 00:11:57,943
Today's meeting minutes.

150
00:11:59,143 --> 00:12:02,343
It took you a whole day on it?

151
00:12:02,343 --> 00:12:05,403
I got scolded for the previous one.

152
00:12:06,623 --> 00:12:08,303
Let me take a look.

153
00:12:08,303 --> 00:12:10,103
Sure.

