00:12:24,383 --> 00:12:27,803
Sister An An, sorry I'm late.

156
00:12:27,803 --> 00:12:30,003
It's fine. I've been waiting.

157
00:12:30,003 --> 00:12:31,544
- Here. 
 - Okay.

158
00:12:32,103 --> 00:12:34,663
I need to pick someone up, so I'll be back late.

159
00:12:34,663 --> 00:12:36,303
Then you'd go.

160
00:12:36,303 --> 00:12:39,583
By the way, how's Lin Tuo's new job?

161
00:12:39,583 --> 00:12:43,763
