162
00:12:43,763 --> 00:12:47,463
Being so busy right away means he's highly valued.

163
00:12:47,463 --> 00:12:50,723
But you're the only one I can rely on now.

164
00:12:50,723 --> 00:12:53,423
Let me know if you find the right job.

165
00:12:53,423 --> 00:12:55,623
- I'll find another part-timer. 
 - Okay.

166
00:12:55,623 --> 00:12:57,523
- All right, then I'll leave. 
 - Just go.

167
00:12:57,523 --> 00:12:59,623
- Okay, bye. 
 - Bye.

