00:14:44,743 --> 00:14:46,143
Where's Beibei?

189
00:14:46,143 --> 00:14:47,903
She is with her mom.

190
00:14:47,903 --> 00:14:49,783
Happy birthday.

191
00:14:49,783 --> 00:14:51,963
It's Lin Tuo's birthday.

192
00:14:51,963 --> 00:14:54,703
- Then tell him for me. 
 - Okay, thank you, Fourth Uncle.

193
00:14:54,703 --> 00:14:57,383
- I'm going in. 
 - Just go.

194
00:15:09,663 --> 00:15:12,203
- Come on, Senior. I'll toast to you. 
 - Come on.

