198
00:15:22,163 --> 00:15:26,623
But honestly, Wei Haiyang is a very excellent designer.

199
00:15:26,623 --> 00:15:30,983
He's also one of the founders of Ji Jia and has a stake in the company.

200
00:15:30,983 --> 00:15:34,683
But he has a strange temper.

201
00:15:34,683 --> 00:15:38,083
He has no interest in management, just focused on design.

202
00:15:38,083 --> 00:15:42,223
But he knows the market so well that even his boss can't control him.

203
00:15:42,223 --> 00:15:46,183
He's the kind of guy who has a big say in Ji Jia.

204
00:15:47,863 --> 00:15:50,323
Chief Designer Wei is quite difficult to get along with.

205
00:15:50,323 --> 00:15:53,443
I've been scolded here for a few days.

206
00:15:53,443 --> 00:15:57,203
He always tells me to leave if I can't stand it.

207
00:15:57,203 --> 00:16:00,283
His two assistant designers have been with him for years.

208
00:16:00,283 --> 00:16:04,863
None of them have turned into designers.

209
00:16:05,903 --> 00:16:09,163
