210
00:16:09,163 --> 00:16:10,723
You'd never know.

211
00:16:10,723 --> 00:16:14,523
All the assistants he's worked with have gone on to be big designers at other companies.

212
00:16:14,523 --> 00:16:18,223
Many companies are waiting to poach his assistants.

213
00:16:19,723 --> 00:16:22,103
