214
00:16:22,103 --> 00:16:26,643
What? You've just been here, and you're already thinking of it?

215
00:16:28,003 --> 00:16:32,503
Don't worry, Mom. I know.

216
00:16:33,183 --> 00:16:37,823
Beibei is pretty good. Enough, the money is enough.

217
00:16:38,883 --> 00:16:43,803
It's my fifth year and I want to do it one last time.

218
00:16:45,443 --> 00:16:50,263
If I don't pass, I won't take it again.

219
00:16:52,523 --> 00:16:56,503
Okay. Mom, take care.

220
00:17:22,743 --> 00:17:25,682
- Sister An An. 
 - Xiao Que.

221
00:17:25,682 --> 00:17:29,563
You don't look right. Are you feeling unwell?

222
00:17:29,563 --> 00:17:33,703
I think I have a little cold.

223
00:17:33,703 --> 00:17:37,383
