224
00:17:38,263 --> 00:17:41,383
Thank you. I'll make that up for you tomorrow.

225
00:17:41,383 --> 00:17:43,263
It's okay. Just go.

226
00:17:43,263 --> 00:17:44,763
I'll take my stuff.

227
00:17:44,763 --> 00:17:47,483
Go to the hospital if you really feel unwell.

228
00:17:55,703 --> 00:17:58,940
 Xiao Que has a cold. I told her to go back early. 

229
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,860
