235
00:18:15,023 --> 00:18:17,063
All right, then take care.

236
00:18:17,063 --> 00:18:19,143
Bye, Senior.

237
00:18:28,703 --> 00:18:30,523
Xiao Que.

238
00:18:35,603 --> 00:18:40,283
- Do you have a fever? 
 - No, just a bit of a cold, and I feel a bit dizzy.

239
00:18:40,283 --> 00:18:42,123
Let me check.

240
00:18:45,343 --> 00:18:48,763
