241
00:18:48,763 --> 00:18:50,603
Not yet.

242
00:18:56,383 --> 00:18:59,123
How did you know I am back?

243
00:18:59,123 --> 00:19:01,863
Sister An An sent me a message, saying you're not feeling well,

244
00:19:01,863 --> 00:19:04,003
so I hurried over.

245
00:19:17,183 --> 00:19:19,363
Drink your medicine first.

246
00:19:35,443 --> 00:19:37,223
What's wrong?

247
00:19:38,043 --> 00:19:41,623
Nothing, I just want to hug you.

248
00:19:44,523 --> 00:19:48,723
I've been so busy at work lately,

249
